result.name: Tong Kong Restaurant

reviews.text: Excellent salted chicken rice. Even the free soup (peanuts/chicken legs) that comes with it is excellent.

The quality of food has remained consistently high for over 10 years we have been coming here. The blanched chicken with ginger spice is a must try, along with chilli salted squid. If you are feeling adventurous there is also deep fried pigs intestines.
They provide very yummy Dongjiang-style chicken, worth to try.
Must try the chicken with ginger and salt
Very tasting chicken! 🍗

result.name: 東江雞食家

reviews.text: 碟頭飯夠大碟😍但成日加價😞
位於大埔廣場，傳统中式飯館， 出名鹽焗雞，扣肉飯都有水準，地方有D窄，衛生麻麻，价錢適中。
最好食當然首推雞飯，梅菜扣肉飯。環店鋪環境就不要要求了。平日午餐時間很多人要等。
要與昆蟲鬥快，約吃太慢隨時有昆蟲飛進湯及餸內
地方太窄，坐位坐得不太舒適，食物質素亦算合格。
